<emph etype = "bold">
B1125: Clutch / Shift Switch Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Inconsistency between signals from CPP No.1 switch or CPP No.2 switch and inhibit switch signal transmitted via CAN communication.
</ptxt>
</entry>
